title: Cant transfer from EUW to OCE - Unknown error
body: Anyone else have this problem? I've just moved back to NZ and am trying to transfer my account which was made in EUW to OCE. My username (not summoners name) was taken; it gives me a prompt and I change my name. I click continue and get an error. wat do?

replies.body: It is most likely because of patch 7.4. Best bet is to wait till after it goes live on both (or better yet all) regions then try again.
